This year has tested us (I call it the year or spiritual warfare), it has tried all of us, and sometimes found us wanting. However, this I know‚Äî one day, when we look back, we can see that God was indeed at work. Wevcan trust God in our now, but when we look back from the future, we can see him at work in our past.

This is not to say that the trials we are currently going through won‚Äôt be fierce and the consequences severe. And yet in this season as in the past, God‚Äôs goodness will prevail. His faithfulness is to a thousand generations. He is the same yesterday, today, and forever. He will make all things new.

